{"tid":470821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"校方安排「學生臨記」背反港獨台詞 遭記者踢爆冇聽李飛講話","createTime":"2017-11-16T16:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T06:28:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":405,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcb215715188c1b92159a7219129cb5c2f8d50e","tid":470821,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"李飛來港宣旨，學校直播，講座後五個學生見記者，合符期望地拋出一大堆反港獨說法，各大新聞日夜loop。<br />\n<br />\n但在主旋律之外，還有些小節想分享。<br />\n<br />\n先提提，當時禮堂內上百學生，出現在記者面前的，只有學校挑選的五人，其他人講座完都被趕鴨仔趕回課室，理所當然地，這些「沉默大多數」的聲音（包括幾位全程沉睡放蚊的同學），在校方操作下都被隔絕於鏡頭以外，而能見諸公眾的，自必是學校眼中的「好學生」。<br />\n<br />\n而同學「分享」之前，校長亦不忌諱，先行對五位同學brief了一番，內容也可想而知。<br />\n<br />\n終於訪問開始，行家順理成章，按李飛的反港獨主題發問。<br />\n<br />\n王同學:「我自己都反對港獨，原則上香港特區行政區係中華人民共和國不可分離一部份。」<br />\n<br />\n同學，你這樣是要應徵外交部發言人嗎？算了，接下來下一位，羅同學。<br />\n<br />\n羅同學:「我就認為青少年俾人誤導&hellip;其實係佢地唔了解基本法而導致產生出黎，如果佢地了解多啲基本法入面條例，可能佢地就唔會有港獨呢個想法。」<br />\n<br />\n熟悉的論調、官樣的用詞，這樣下去，所謂的同學「見記者」就可以在一片和諧中落幕。可惜記者天性愛找人麻煩，總是愛在主調中尋找不協調。<br />\n<br />\n「同學，你介唔介意覆述下，頭先李飛主任係港獨呢個部份，實際上係講咗啲咩?」<br />\n<br />\n羅同學:「我&hellip;聽得唔係好清楚&hellip;無咩太留意。」<br />\n<br />\n「即係你唔知李飛講咗啲咩，但係又咁樣答問題?」<br />\n<br />\n羅同學:「係既&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n臨時演員都是演員，有點職業道德好嗎？這樣是沒有飯盒吃的。也罷，下一位。<br />\n<br />\n林同學:「港獨呢啲野我唔係好鐘意&hellip;啲年輕人就唔知真正情況係咩，就聽啲謠言自己去揣摩一啲唔好嘅野&hellip;希望佢地認真讀好啲書，認識多啲憲法基本法，呢啲問題就可以減少。」<br />\n<br />\n少年，作為一個中三學生，你口中的「啲年輕人」是誰呢？讀好書就反港獨是甚麼邏輯？算了，不想再問。然後學校老師打圓場，同學們虛應幾句，雖然聽不大明白，但覺得活動很有意義云云，三幾個問題，前後約10分鐘，鬧劇結束。<br />\n<br />\n不想太苛責學生，畢竟他們只是食物鏈中最底層，整場李飛大會，北京壓港府、港府壓學校、學校壓老師、老師壓學生，大家都不過在敷衍交數。<br />\n<br />\n或許整件事最有教育意義的是，讓學生早早明白社會現實：世間萬事皆虛、唯獨權力為真。<br />\n<br />\n學子無辜，卻難為那些以教育工作者自居的，還敢說一切都是出於「專業」判斷，說學校不應被政治干預云云，又死活說不出，李飛講話教育意義何在。<br />\n<br />\n也不知是可笑或可悲，直播李飛演講的禮堂一旁，立了一個孔子像，曾經被共產黨弄得死去活來的孔夫子，在李飛的陰影下被樹立著。<br />\n<br />\n孔曰，君子謀道不謀食，憂道不憂貧。<br />\n<br />\n孔曰，損者三友，友便辟，友善柔，友便佞，損矣。<br />\n<br />\n立其像而忘其誨，還好孔子遠鬼神，否則泉下有知，不知作何感想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/直播李飛演講的禮堂一旁-立了一個孔子像/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E6%9D%8E%E9%A3%9B%E6%BC%94%E8%AC%9B%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%AE%E5%A0%82%E4%B8%80%E6%97%81-%E7%AB%8B%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%AD%94%E5%AD%90%E5%83%8F%2F&d=q81vSNv%2F1E6q%2FqP0JqdngsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=65b32ec5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD%E6%9D%8E%E9%A3%9B%E6%BC%94%E8%AC%9B%E7%9A%84%E7%A6%AE%E5%A0%82%E4%B8%80%E6%97%81-%E7%AB%8B%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%AD%94%E5%AD%90%E5%83%8F%2F&h=86ec3ced\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/直播李飛演講的禮堂一旁-立了一個孔子像/</a>"},{"pid":"a93a02a809765f331edf07f0c7bacfcca2192e23","tid":470821,"uid":22858,"like":40,"dislike":6,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、民國復興、群龍共舞、優美開始、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、JR、RedBaron (Epiphany)、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1e9276e0462d505aa3e428b36ed290635cdfffd8","tid":470821,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839d317f53c94372fcc2abb0ed75cee895a99a57","tid":470821,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc83ea69165bdfd687a63298c523a00839d2f96","tid":470821,"uid":11895,"like":141,"dislike":1,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"讀書先會搞港獨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701a289501ae58c80fffbff70a032e3d1d4cf079","tid":470821,"uid":36178,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:26:35.000Z","msg":"成年人編嘅劇本都唔撚係以年青後生仔思想出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c94a9efa129942ed68c6d375dd1360c37a0942f","tid":470821,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"孔子像？<br />\n<br />\n孔教學院?"},{"pid":"66e4551946834e6ddfe51438c03258ae86ff27a3","tid":470821,"uid":6752,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成年人編嘅劇本都唔撚係以年青後生仔思想出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n語境0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話老師,作文都唔識作"},{"pid":"8debb28c35ab2eecb114786dcd7b07021e4869fe","tid":470821,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成年人編嘅劇本都唔撚係以年青後生仔思想出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n語境0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話老師,作文都唔識作</blockquote><br />\n老師無資格作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6555bc48ed0876e266754dca7df0355fe4a6824a","tid":470821,"uid":38671,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成年人編嘅劇本都唔撚係以年青後生仔思想出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n語境0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話老師,作文都唔識作</blockquote><br />\n老師無資格作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港上一代人係英治溫室長大<br />\n做左幾十年人政治智慧隨時低過呢幾年經歷咁多政治事件既後生仔<br />\n班柒頭淨係識擦鞋而且係亂咁擦"},{"pid":"28a5df02d808dfa03ceaa74a8df5c0efcfebe12b","tid":470821,"uid":1430,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"中三學生：d年輕人....<br />\n我在場都會聽到黑人問號啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 度稿果個可唔可以專業d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e731f7497a17540f1bfe040a5e7437fdfc350a","tid":470821,"uid":550,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成年人編嘅劇本都唔撚係以年青後生仔思想出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n語境0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話老師,作文都唔識作</blockquote><br />\n叫班鳩毛都未出齊嘅細路屌鳩年輕人有冇說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15061a7e6f880579fb47b99e91502bd531cae57","tid":470821,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"電視睇左林同學發言一段，又係可以放入「柒到唔敢睇」系列"},{"pid":"b50f48e096c08302404c7f317575a4dc9842042e","tid":470821,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"夠薑瞓覺個幾個學生好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然一定俾條奶共校長屌到仆街都照抗命<br />\n將來必成大器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba9b4c83a298fef6b555989403095a8f6ec9fe9","tid":470821,"uid":14188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:39:29.000Z","msg":"有無片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2049d34064ccfd40d38c627740e7dbadd00c31f9","tid":470821,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成年人編嘅劇本都唔撚係以年青後生仔思想出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n語境0分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話老師,作文都唔識作</blockquote><br />\n老師無資格作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港上一代人係英治溫室長大<br />\n做左幾十年人政治智慧隨時低過呢幾年經歷咁多政治事件既後生仔<br />\n班柒頭淨係識擦鞋而且係亂咁擦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家要鬥爆seed，建制裡面都係要咁，唔係d京官識你班建制派係乜水<br />\n<br />\n喇，長毛、黃之鋒唔洗點做咩，已經入哂習近平腦海，所以建制恨之入骨"},{"pid":"b3559a672d5175d03c6178d4d8a144b979c9be26","tid":470821,"uid":5195,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:40:33.000Z","msg":"政府基本法推廣督導委員會今日舉辦《基本法》研討會，邀請全國人大常委會基本法委員會主任李飛來港發表演說。教育局上月就此發出通告，邀請各辦學團體安排屬下中學在校內觀看直播，有約50間中學參與，包括在葵芳的獅子會中學。<br />\n<br />\n獅子會中學安排了中三、中五及中六共4班，共百多名學生在禮堂看早上10時的直播。通識科主任江健榮在直播前向學生講解《基本法》的背景、與憲法與的關係等資料。江健榮指，香港的年青人與國家領導人對《基本法》有不同看法，希望學生了解兩種看法，從而明白何為有爭議出現。李飛的演說長達50分鐘，有學生邊聽邊抄筆記，亦有學生中途打呵欠、打瞌睡。<br />\n<br />\n記者於直播結束後在校外訪問學生，大部分沒看直播的學生似乎不太清楚李飛演說一事，有人反問記者：「咩嚟㗎？」有人指：「我連邊個係李飛都唔知。」、「淨係中六可以聽。」有學生被記者問到有否聽李飛演說，回答：「X佢老母！」有未獲安排聽直播的中六學生表示：「我都唔想聽，上堂重要過聽佢講嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n獅子會中學安排百多名學生在禮堂看李飛演講直播，部分學生低頭、打呵欠。<br />\n就讀中五的陳同學，他所屬的班別沒有獲安排到禮堂看直播，他趁午飯時間自行上網聽了部分內容。他認為演說與學習相關，故有興趣去聽，他表示自己是中立，但聽完覺得「冇得著」。被問到有沒有李飛的觀點他是認同的，他直言：「冇。」<br />\n<br />\n陳同學聽到李飛促訂立《基本法》23條，坦言：「梗係擔心啦，立咗就麻煩，唔知追溯期啲嘢嘛。」他個人不認同23條立法。至於港獨的部分，他指未有聽到。<br />\n<br />\n陳同學表示，學校「大費干戈」調動課堂搞直播不太好，做法影響學生上課。他承認演說內容他不完全聽得明白，「明晒就唔係讀中學啦。」<br />\n<br />\n有中四學生對記者表示想聽李飛直播，他解釋：「因為係國家大事，佢係國家高層。」但被問到李飛的職銜、職責範疇，他就一律答：「唔知喎。」"},{"pid":"9d977b206b73918547f1f58ca06b4dee3251ddfc","tid":470821,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"記者午飯時間在校外採訪期間，校長林日豐特地出來對記者說：「到呢度為止啦，唔想件事複雜化。」記者解釋希望詢問學生的看法，他顯得不耐煩：「我諗頭先都講得好清楚，唔知你係咪唔明我講咩啦。到呢度為止啦，好嗎？」說罷，他一直站在校門外，直至記者離開。<br />\n<br />\n在直播演說後，學校安排了兩名中三、兩名中五及一名中六學生在禮堂見記者，他們普遍對李飛的演說態度正面，但指因為是普通話演講，而且內容較深，未能完全明白。中五學生王浩然認同學校的安排，認為李飛的演說內容切合學習內容，又指香港學生知道祖國歷史是重要的。<br />\n<br />\n中六學生陳雋禧指，演說令他學到《基本法》與憲法的關係，例如他更加明白要在一國之下才有兩制。被問到對李飛講港獨的看法，他指，很多年輕人不了解《基本法》才受誤導。記者請他複述李飛相關部分的演說內容，他卻未能複述。<br />\n<br />\n中五學生劉欣諾指，她基本上認同李飛演說的內容，最深刻的是他說《基本法》僅次於憲法，她表示有關說法令她不明白《基本法》訂立的意義，故印象深刻。<br />\n<br />\n學校向觀看直播的學生派發工作紙，學生要回答4條問題，包括：「甚麼是憲法？」、「《基本法》在中國及香港有何法律地位？」、「《基本法》對一國兩制的落實有甚麼意義呢？」、「《基本法》對維持香港繁榮穩定起了甚麼作用？」。記者問中五學生王浩然怎樣作答，他指自己的普通話不太好，主要靠課堂所學填寫答案，未有透露具體作答內容。"},{"pid":"a4ebad59e5f9dbc0dc027e1fc9cb39ccf86f9eb6","tid":470821,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠薑瞓覺個幾個學生好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然一定俾條奶共校長屌到仆街都照抗命<br />\n將來必成大器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽講話中6dse學生都要晒時間去聽, 都黐鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f479eae13f8144897c49d91d9181399b5d3a2","tid":470821,"uid":28195,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/004447_964fcdbc8a823f64b9ff2acd82ddfb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F004447_964fcdbc8a823f64b9ff2acd82ddfb2e.jpg&h=f8e8aaca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線真係放出黎，back 已 up"},{"pid":"fa4a0806dce3ec0a0496ec904b89ef5002ed79ac","tid":470821,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/004447_964fcdbc8a823f64b9ff2acd82ddfb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F004447_964fcdbc8a823f64b9ff2acd82ddfb2e.jpg&h=f8e8aaca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線真係放出黎，back 已 up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n補link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/759386584253412/\" data-sr-url=\"h